Package: RcppKPCA
Title: Fast Kernel PCA using Rcpp and Armadillo
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Javdat", "Umarov", email = "lovable_residue6j@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Author: Javdat Umarov [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Javdat Umarov <lovable_residue6j@icloud.com>
Description: A computationally efficient implementation of Kernel Principal Component 
    Analysis (KPCA) using the Gaussian (RBF) kernel. The package leverages 'Rcpp' and 
    the 'Armadillo' C++ library for fast matrix operations to significantly speed up 
    the kernel matrix computation, centering, and eigendecomposition steps of the 
    KPCA algorithm. Includes methods for projecting new data points onto existing 
    kernel principal components.
License: GPL-3
